OL,3,CMan's arms 'completely exploded' after
OL,4,Ctouching 11,000 volts of electricity
OL,6,F*This article contains images of
OL,7,FDarren Harris's third degree burns*
OL,9,FDarren Harris has been described as a
OL,10,F'walking miracle' after suffering
OL,11,Fthird degree burns over half of his
OL,12,Fbody after touching live electricity
OL,13,Fcables carrying 11,000 volts.
OL,15,FIn 2020, Darren was inside an
OL,16,Fabandoned building in Wolverhampton,
OL,17,Flooking for illegal scrap metal,
OL,18,Fafter, in his words, 'struggling for
OL,19,Ffunds' during lockdown.
