OL,3,CMan's arms 'completely exploded' after
OL,4,Ctouching 11,000 volts of electricity
OL,6,FHe assumed the power to the building
OL,7,Fwas off, as it was due to be
OL,8,Fdemolished, but when he put his left
OL,9,Farm on the 11,000 volt switchboard it
OL,10,Fcompletely melted his forearms to the
OL,11,Fbone.
OL,13,FHe was knocked out by the force of the
OL,14,Felectricity but remarkably despite the
OL,15,Fpain he was in, Darren managed to
OL,16,Fsprint out of the building. He said,
OL,18,F"I ran in front of the ambulance on
OL,19,Fits way to me to flag it down and both
OL,20,Ffaces of the paramedics were as white
OL,21,Fas a ghost."
