OL,3,CMan's arms 'completely exploded' after
OL,4,Ctouching 11,000 volts of electricity
OL,6,FThe paramedics who were first on the
OL,7,Fscene have just met up with Darren
OL,8,Ffour years on, and say it's a miracle
OL,9,Fhe even left hospital.
OL,11,FDr Richard Fawcett said: "Anything
OL,12,Fwhere you get this massive surge of
OL,13,Felectrical current going through the
OL,14,Fbody causing such extensive tissue
OL,15,Finjury, the likelihood is you're
OL,16,Fprobably not going to leave hospital.
OL,17,FSo to see Darren a few years later
OL,18,Fdoing so fantastically well is
OL,19,Funbelievable."
