OL,3,CMan's arms 'completely exploded' after
OL,4,Ctouching 11,000 volts of electricity
OL,6,FParamedic Gary Williams said: "Matt
OL,7,Fand I both looked at each other and
OL,8,Fsaid where do we start? Darren's arms
OL,9,Fhad completely exploded."
OL,11,FDespite being uncertain about if he'd
OL,12,Fever be physically fit enough, he's
OL,13,Fmanaged to return to full time work
OL,14,Fand is self-employed as a scaffolder.
OL,16,FHe's raised money for the Katy Piper
OL,17,FFoundation which supports people
OL,18,Fliving with burns injuries by doing a
OL,19,Fskydive and is a keen gym-goer.
