OL,3,CMan's arms 'completely exploded' after
OL,4,Ctouching 11,000 volts of electricity
OL,6,FHe says, "I'm still here today,
OL,7,Fshining and trying to rebuild my life
OL,8,Fthe best I can.
OL,10,F"I've rebuilt my character and my
OL,11,Fcareer, I've been given a second
OL,12,Fchance at life and I'm grateful to be
OL,13,Fhere.
OL,15,F"I want to tell my story and inspire
OL,16,Fpeople and show them that they can get
OL,17,Fthrough the hardest thing in their
OL,18,Flives and still come out the other
OL,19,Fside."
